unittitle.value: Records of the Office of the Vice President for University Relations (John J. O'Connor)

abstract.value: This collection documents John J. O'Connor's tenure at NYU as Assistant to the Vice President for External Affairs and Associate Vice President for External Affairs. It also includes some records from his work as Vice President for University Relations. The colleciton is unprocessed.

p.value: Please contact the University Archivist with specific questions regarding restrictions.

Identification of item, date (if known); Records of the Office of the Vice President for University Relations (John J. O'Connor); RG 7.2; box number; folder number; New York University Archives, New York University.
<list><item>Administration, Archives H, NYU Archives</item><item>Faculty Handbook, 1982, NYU Archives</item></list>

This collection documents O'Connor's tenure as Assistant to the Vice President for External Affairs and Associate Vice President for External Affairs. It also includes some records from his work as Vice President for University Relations. The colleciton is unprocessed.
